Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的隊伍贏得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士岡選拔賽的第三名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且取得參加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本決賽的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正朝著決賽的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道出發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太高興了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個時候狀況突發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點沒被嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是昏倒還嚇倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們已經取得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參賽資格了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我到現在還不敢相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的目標就是把這個超級駕駛執照弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是最沒有信心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你儘管取笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表現真是太好了,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五話  目標 全日本錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹,良平,伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上五人的聲紋記錄完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了以上五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以操縱本車之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都必須要證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我這個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的駕駛技術進步很多耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為他有機車賽的經驗才進步這麼快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過技術還是太差了,必須要再多加磨練才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒說得蠻直接的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下,隼人可是眾人期待的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要太傷人心好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我聽了不太高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是「阿斯拉達」說的也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有今天的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是我的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都多虧了「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它對我的忠告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 良平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快把工作做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那裏以後立刻開始檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我車子的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先,因為有人不太瞭解我硬要開上土堆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸收了不少砂土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些砂土還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我的冷卻器裏面的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上為了糊塗生手亂開車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的軀動系統也損害了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是不適當的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成齒輪相當大的磨損
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什麼口氣嘛 「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是報告損害的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有責怪你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好像是在責怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成目前的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你亂駕駛的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點也不討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次講話都讓人氣得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,隼人 別在這裏搗蛋好不好 去做你該做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」,還有別的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 別在那裏閒著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一些可能要用的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」已把新條直輝的駕駛過程都記錄下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以先模擬訓練一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」可以把新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在富士岡比賽的過程重現一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～這種事也能做到啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為「阿斯拉達」的系統比較特別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請講話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教 「阿斯拉達」老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認無誤 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把新條直輝的駕駛過程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才踩煞車的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比新條直輝要早一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當時比我晚了一點是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的好平順喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 如果說我也能夠像他這樣駕駛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以更快點了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以更快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6900元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他弄錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差2500元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?漲價啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面那部車說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的費用由你們來付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來個三文治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再加漢堡飽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要加青椒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都給我吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們大家都給我安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關即將舉行的全國錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有兩位邀請的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手抵達了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說全國錦標賽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達的這兩位選手是德國的法蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美國的積奇選手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們終於來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問兩位對這次的比賽有什麼樣的意見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有什麼感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是對日本的高智能方程式非常感到興趣很想見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的小姐們 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏向各位介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位選手目前的戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我們來看看法蘭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去年的世界排名是第三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時他還是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位優秀的汽車設計者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年他轉到了SGM車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定駕駛的是自己所設計的新車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雪鐵」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於積奇選手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在印地500米的賽車當中 當時他只有十五歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年世界排名第五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的車輛是「史巴比安」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我們剛得到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今天兩點鐘左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了一件綁架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯目前正朝東北方向逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而警方也布下了警網正展開全面的追查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這附近耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安真差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從那裏來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐那車子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剛剛那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要叫他還錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!那個那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方目前已經公開的搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且呼籲市民要協助警方調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再重覆一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架的是一名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫由莉的五歲小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在公園附近玩耍時…是這女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他就是嫌犯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我去報警
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這別走 不要亂跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 良平 你們兩個跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警察來以前我們要先把那小子給抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子還我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個男的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂動我的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把車子還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部車子是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費盡精神和心血打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「阿斯拉達」開出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲紋確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這裏並不是賽車場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還在保養當中不能出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩都被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總不能見死不救吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口,我說要去就是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快上車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止「阿斯拉達」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂你的問話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請明確一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是一般的電腦車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是高智能方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會坐上這種車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但把我當成了犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把我的車子給弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然也會開著高智能方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種小鬼莫非你也是個賽車手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情等下再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先救小女孩要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的車子弄壞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會饒過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可不是賽車場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 警察來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要交給警方去辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停車投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調整成讓我容易點行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 馬上調整
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤 油門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煞車 輔助系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 不晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 原來我說的話電腦也聽得懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們追來了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想捉到我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿!活該!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 喂,想辦法甩掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動煙霧系統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不愧是高智能方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 後面的警車就麻煩你照顧一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 警車怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 那個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在也只好自己去抓那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說你是個小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子只要一撞上它不就自動停下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦!那個小女孩還在車上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車上有安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦 快點把前面的地圖拿給我看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了沒有 電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉!我無法聽從你的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看一下前面的地圖怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道,檢視前方地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」它只聽我一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個彎道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們後輪去撞對方的前輪這樣它就會停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們的外側去撞它 準沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們能夠開到彎道的內側與前車之間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以使損害降到最小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣得事真的能做到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你害怕的話 那就我來開呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你說過了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只聽我一個人的指揮不會聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這個車真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦!「阿斯拉達」拜託幫我算算看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按照剛才我所說的方法去做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那前面那個車子的損害到底有多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 照他的話去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 馬上計算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面那部車應該
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會受到輕微的損害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果安全裝置有啟動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的機率不到1%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到他前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…電腦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續往前衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 立刻加速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渦輪加速啟動,引擊臨界點倒數開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能再快一點了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渦輪加速啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋還挺不賴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線恐怕沒有辦法超過我的車喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那邊臭美了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要進入彎道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心!這小子進入彎道以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就會減速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 我們只要一踩煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以從外側超過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 車子會打轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照著做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高速啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩煞車還太早了,相信這車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 撞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然弄壞了我的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的車弄成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先拿我的修理費
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我修理費的收據,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女孩沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要拿回我的車子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘了剛才我跟你借的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過路費
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像對閃電車非常的熟悉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都是賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靠那個人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煞車的時候才能恰到好處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能幹 不過不是很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是碰撞賽車的技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰撞賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉著互相碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒對方的一種賽車方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說剛才那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種賽車手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 絕對不能再有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次像這樣子胡搞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所參加的是正規的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要有賽車手的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天干的還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女孩也平安沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 回收「阿斯拉達」後出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

